



Basic Data Tables
=====
Users
Permissions
Roles
 
User has one to many Permissions
User has one Role
Roles have one to many Permissions
 
 
Users
	id
	first_name
	last_name
	email_address
	created_at
	role_id

Permissions
	id
	name
	code (or some readable unique identifier like a snake cased version of the name that can be used when decorating actions to check for proper permissions instead of decorating with numeric IDs)
	description

Roles
	id
	name
	description





https://computerlab.io/2016/08/17/django-rest-framework-roles/
ACLs https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Access_control_list

https://github.com/vintasoftware/django-role-permissions/blob/master/setup.py

